translation.en: Like the prophet Habakkuk, sometimes I want to shout, "Why do you make me see wrong-doing and look at trouble?"
translation.zu: Ngokwesibonelo, umprofethi uHabakuki wabuza uJehova: "Kungani ungenza ngibone okulimazayo, futhi uqhubeka ubheke inkathazo nje?

translation.en: A description doesn't do it justice; it's a vision of a female demon.
translation.zu: Isinqumo esingenacala kakhulu - umlingiswa wesifazane uvele nje ekhona ngokoqobo.

translation.en: There is a lot to see and do in Accra.
translation.zu: Kuningi ongakubona futhi ukwenze eMarrakech.
